Preheat an air fryer to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).

Place @okra{1⁄2%pound}, @olive oil{1%teaspoon}, @salt{1⁄4%teaspoon}, and @pepper{1%teaspoon} in a bowl; stir gently to coat. Arrange @okra{1⁄2%pound} in a single layer in the air fryer basket.

Cook in the preheated air fryer for 10 minutes, tossing the basket halfway.

Remove the basket and toss @okra{1⁄2%pound} again; continue to cook until crispy, about 2 minutes more. Serve immediately.